              <p>Arvind Bellad is an entrepreneur turned politician. He represents Hubli-Dharwad constituency in Karnataka Legislative Assembly as a BJP MLA. <br>
                <br>
                Youngest among his siblings, Arvind was a bright student and earned Bachelor of Engineering from SDM College of Engineering, Dharwad, Karnataka and then further moved to France to earn a Post Graduate Diploma in Management from INSEAD, France. <br>
                <br>
                Arvind Bellad is a successful businessman, owning sugar factories and shares in many other business ventures. He debuted into active politics as a BJP MLA from Hubli-Dharwad constituency in the year 2013 and retained his seat in 2018 election as well. <br>
                <br>
                Bellad considered to be a progressive politician and popular for his unique ideas and welfare campaigns. He got massive support of all corners of his constituency and state for the campaigns like Namma Mane – Namma Bellad and Namma Krishi – Namma Bellad.
